          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0642P0-02927'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0642P0_20021218_GCR_156' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
